# SMBBackupPlugin  
Back up to an SMB server

# üåê Nebulix SMBBackupPlugin - Backup Plugin for Paper 1.20 to 1.21

**Nebulix SMBBackupPlugin** is a high-functionality backup plugin compatible with **Paper 1.20 to 1.21**,  
which allows automatic and manual backups of world data or any directories to an **SMB (Samba) server**.

---

## ‚ú® Key Features

‚úÖ **Automatic and manual backups to an SMB server**  
‚úÖ **Scheduled backups using cron format**  
‚úÖ **Supports worlds and multiple arbitrary directories**  
‚úÖ **Immediate backup with `/backup now` command**  
‚úÖ **Displays estimated time, file count, and size before backup**  
‚úÖ **Checks and warns about SMB server free space (quota)**  
‚úÖ **Convenient commands like `/backup reload` and `/backup status`**  
‚úÖ **Compatible with Paper 1.20.x to 1.21.x**

